      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The papers contain a one page description of "Ship of
         Fools" signed by Porter; a section of the novel as it appeared
         in "Mademoiselle" with brief revisions by Porter; a tearsheet
         of proof from "Mademoiselle" with two autograph revisions and
         notes by Porter, and a note from Cyrilly Abels; and the
         covering envelope for the above addressed to Floyd
         Stovall.</p>
      </scopecontent>
